condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section II, Part A, para 1 | Description :Shandong shall monitor and evaluate project progress andprepare project reports semi-annually starting March 15, 2012 | Frequency :SemiAnnual
Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section II, Part A, para 2 | Description :Carry out mid-term review | Due Date :15-Sep-2014

Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section II, Part B, para 2 | Description :Have financial statements audited by independentauditors and submit audits to Bank six months after close of monitoring period | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section IV, para (b) | Description :Issue regulations adopting the guidelines for old citiesregeneration and development control | Due Date :01-Jan-2012

Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section IV, para (d) | Description :Starting Jan. 1, 2012, each year, increase respective annualbudget provisions for operation and maintenance of cultural heritage in Qufu & Zoucheng by at least 10%, with 2011 as baseline |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Project Agreement (PA), Schedule, Section I, Part C, para 3 | Description :Maintain policies and procedures forM&E; prepare semi-annual progress reports on status of compliance with EMPs and RAPs | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement: PA, Schedule, Section IV, para (c).Description: Prior to the development of the city block with Gupan pond inQufu Ming Old City, and the Three Street Blocks in Zoucheng Old City, submit to the Bank for review and comments, the developmentplan and design proposals for such blocks.
